Devops is more about set of processes that correlate to bring development teams and processes to support doftware development.
The important reason behind the devops popularity is that it healps enterprises to build and enhance products at quicker pace than traditional
software development methods.

The major reasons to adopt Devops are 
Faster innovations
Shorter development cycle 
Reduced deployment failuers 
Improvede communication and collaboration
more stable operating environments
Increased efficiencies 
Reduce cost and IT head count.
